## 6. Testing & Quality Assurance Plan
- **Unit Testing:** Validate conversion mathematics, input sanitization, and date calculation helper functions using Vitest.
- **Accessibility Audit:** Keyboard-only navigation walk-through, verifying focus does not get trapped. Use `axe-core` / Lighthouse to run accessibility tests.
- **Responsive Testing:** Verify rendering on screen widths from 320px (mobile) to 1920px (desktop), ensuring tables wrap gracefully.
